.304 2.464h0.036c1.946 0 3.804-1.357 5.304-2.464 2.911-2.107 5.911-4.143 8.893-6.161 0.643-0.446 1.25-0.964 1.786-1.554zM32 7.714c0 2-1.482 3.804-3.054 4.893-2.786 1.929-5.589 3.857-8.357 5.804-1.161 0.804-3.125 2.446-4.571 2.446h-0.036c-1.446 0-3.411-1.643-4.571-2.446-2.768-1.946-5.571-3.875-8.339-5.804-1.268-0.857-3.071-2.875-3.071-4.5 0-1.75 0.946-3.25 2.857-3.25h26.286c1.554 0 2.857 1.286 2.857 2.857z"></path> <a href="#" aria-label="Email" data-ss-ss-link="mailto:?body=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.visualcapitalist.com%2Ffeed%2F&#038;subject=The%20Lithium%20Rush%3A%20Can%20We%20Meet%20Tomorrow%E2%80%99s%20Lithium%20Demand%3F" class="ss-envelope-color" rel="nofollow noopener" data-ss-ss-network-id="envelope" data-ss-ss-post-id="161653" data-ss-ss-location="inline_content" data-ss-ss-permalink="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/feed/" data-ss-ss-type="share"><span class="ss-share-network-content"><span class="ss-reveal-label-wrap"><span class="ss-network-label">电子邮件</span></span></span></a></li></ul></div></div><div class="vce-sponsor-disclaimer"><span class="vce-sponsor-disclaimer-text">以下内容由<a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/company_spotlight/energyx/?utm_source=VC&amp;utm_medium=spon-con&amp;utm_campaign=company-spotlight" class="vce-sponsor-disclaimer-link" target="_blank">EnergyX</a>赞助</span></div><div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div><div class="vce-full-width-viz"> <a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/company_spotlight/energyx/?utm_source=VC&#038;utm_medium=spon-con&#038;utm_campaign=company-spotlight" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/BC_VC_EnergyX_Tomorrows-Lithium-Demand_25102023-2.jpg" alt="显示 2030 年锂需求的图表"></a> </div><div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex"><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:70%"><h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>我们能满足明天的锂需求吗？</strong></h2><p>锂是世界上最重要的自然资源之一，对于我们推动可持续能源至关重要。</p><p>在这张由<a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/company_spotlight/energyx/?utm_source=VC&amp;utm_medium=spon-con&amp;utm_campaign=company-spotlight" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">EnergyX</a>赞助的图表中，我们提出了一个问题：预计到 2030 年，全球<strong>电动汽车销量将超过 3.5 亿辆</strong>，我们能否满足明天的锂需求？</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>解决明天的锂问题</strong></h2><p>为电动汽车电池提供动力的锂是从五彩盐湖或硬岩中发现的化合物中提炼出来的，其数量以碳酸锂当量（LCE）来衡量。</p><p>因此，为了为全球生产的大量电动汽车提供动力，需要持续、可靠的锂供应。然而，预计到2030年年需求增长高达20%，目前的<a href="https://www.mckinsey.com/industries/metals-and-mining/our-insights/australias-potential-in-the-lithium-market" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">锂供应量</a>将不足以满足需求，需要的量将增加<strong>近一倍</strong>。 </p><table id="tablepress-3612" class="tablepress tablepress-id-3612"><thead><tr class="row-1 odd"><th class="column-1">年</th><th class="column-2">全球LCE供应量（吨）</th><th class="column-3">全球LCE需求（吨）</th></tr></thead><tbody class="row-hover"><tr class="row-2 even"><td class="column-1"> 2022年</td><td class="column-2">750,000</td><td class="column-3"> 720,000</td></tr><tr class="row-3 odd"><td class="column-1"> 2030年</td><td class="column-2">1,640,000</td><td class="column-3"> 3,060,000</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>提取解决方案</strong></h2><p>锂需求如此严重地超过供应的主要原因之一是传统的<a href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/visualizing-25-years-of-lithium-production-by-country/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">锂提取</a>方法缓慢、过时，并且经常造成环境危害。然而，一种称为直接锂提取（DLE）的新锂提取方法可以解决供应问题。</p><p> DLE的锂回收率高达90%，比传统工艺高出<strong>300%</strong> 。该工艺还可以从以前未开发的资源中提取锂，包括加利福尼亚州和阿肯色州的斯马科弗地区。</p><p>此外，DLE 效率极高，仅需两天即可处理锂矿，而这一过程通常需要 18 个月。该工艺也更加环保，因为生产一吨锂通常需要超过<a href="https://www.euronews.com/green/2022/02/01/south-america-s-lithium-fields-reveal-the-dark-side-of-our-electric-future" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">220 万升淡水</a>，而 DLE 需要的数量很少。</p><h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>前进之路</strong></h2><p>没有行动，<strong> </strong>到2030年，锂将无法满足清洁能源转型和联合国可持续发展目标的综合需求。</p><p>然而，EnergyX 等先驱公司在 DLE 方面的进步可以帮助满足需求并确保向更可持续的未来过渡。 </p><div class="vc-info-box"><img decoding="async" style="max-width:28px;" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/logo.png" alt="视觉资本主义标志" class="vc-info-icon"><p class="vc-info-box-text">准备好加入能源转型了吗？ <a href =https://www.visualcapitalist.com/company_spotlight/energyx/?utm_source=VC&#038;utm_medium=spon-con&#038;utm_campaign=company-spotlight>在此处</a>了解有关 EnergyX 的更多信息。</p></div> <a class="vc-newsletter" href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/subscribe/"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1216" src="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/footer-email.gif" alt="订阅视觉资本家" /></a> <div class="wpforms-container wpforms-container-full vc-subscribe-post" id="wpforms-140438"><form id="wpforms-form-140438" class="wpforms-validate wpforms-form wpforms-ajax-form" data-formid="140438" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/feed/" data-token="5a1430f8a197ec175eb2b3d24b326959"><noscript class="wpforms-error-noscript">请在您的浏览器中启用 JavaScript 以完成此表格。 </noscript><div class="wpforms-field-container"><div id="wpforms-140438-field_1-container" class="wpforms-field wpforms-field-email vc-subscribe-post-email" data-field-id="1"><label class="wpforms-field-label" for="wpforms-140438-field_1">喜欢上面的数据可视化吗？ <span class="wpforms-required-label">*</span></label> <input type="email" id="wpforms-140438-field_1" class="wpforms-field-large wpforms-field-required" name="wpforms[fields][1]" placeholder="Your email address" spellcheck="false" required></div></div><!-- .wpforms-field-container --><div class="wpforms-submit-container" ><input type="hidden" name="wpforms[id]" value="140438"><input type="hidden" name="wpforms[author]" value="1116"> <button type="submit" name="wpforms[submit]" id="wpforms-submit-140438" class="wpforms-submit vc-subscribe-post-button" data-alt-text="Sending..." data-submit-text="Subscribe" aria-live="assertive" value="