opener" target="_blank">BBC</a>报道，圭亚那拥有超过110亿桶石油储量。</p><p>这篇文章<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com/ranked-the-fastest-growing-economies-in-2024/">排名：2024 年增长最快的经济体</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.visualcapitalist.com">Visual Capitalist</a>上。</p> ; https://www.visualcapitalist.com/ranked-the-fastest-forming-economies-in-2024/feed/ 0 161677
